text: Rob Kardashian's Adorable New Video of Daughter Dream Will Make Your Heart Melt by Antoinette Bueno 1:35   Playing Rob Kardashian's Adorable New Video of Daughter Dream Will Make Your Heart Melt Rob Kardashian is enjoying being a doting father. The 29-year-old reality star Instagrammed a super cute video of his daughter, Dream, on Monday, using Snapchat's dog filter. Rob and his fiancee, Blac Chyna, welcomed Dream in November. üòçüòç A video posted by ROBERT KARDASHIAN (@robkardashian) on Jan 9, 2017 at 7:31pm PST A photo posted by ROBERT KARDASHIAN (@robkardashian) on Jan 4, 2017 at 8:16pm PST A photo posted by ROBERT KARDASHIAN (@robkardashian) on Jan 3, 2017 at 10:25pm PST Meanwhile, Chyna recently hung out with Rob's sister Khloe Kardashian's ex-boyfriend, French Montana. The "Pop That" rapper Instagrammed a pic of the two having fun on the set of what appears to be a new music video alongside singer The Weeknd. Last week, a source told ET that Rob and Chyna are "back together and focusing on their relationship" after their social media drama last month, and after they skipped the Kardashian Christmas Eve celebration. "It's safe to say Chyna and Rob took some time off to focus on their immediate family," the source said. "It's not a bad thing, and they needed a break for themselves, and their daughter."
